               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. SERJEANT PARRY</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> How often have you smelt it before 5 o'clock in the morning? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> I have worked three or four mornings in the week, and have smelt it when they have been boiling.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
