                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Is there a steam engine at Mr. Burgess's? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes—I have seen the smoke coming out of the chimney into the rope ground—Mr. Burgess's factory has not at all affected the atmosphere.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18570706-name-381" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18570706-name-381" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18570706-name-381" type="surname" value="SULLIVAN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18570706-name-381" type="given" value="MICHAEL"></interp>MICHAEL SULLIVAN</persName>
                  </hi>. I have lived upwards of nine months in Blue Anchor lane, about 300 yards from Mr. Burgess's—I have never experienced any inconvenience in my house—I have gone close to the factory at different times by night as well as day, and have never smelt any unpleasant smells.</p>
               <p>
