                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> How long did you work at Mr. Burgess's? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Perhaps about two months, off and on, not constantly—I had an oppor<lb></lb>tunity of seeing the heap of gas finings; it was no disagreeable smell—I have seen the copper used, and did not smell any disagreeable or annoying smell; nor from the extractors—it is impossible from the extractors—I knew a manure place, and sometimes there has been disagreeable smells—I have walked by it, but it is closed up now—there are some smells from the arches.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
